* B. Marcus Priteca (1889–1971), theatre architect
* Sir Basil Spence (1907–1976), architect of Coventry Cathedral and the New Zealand Parliament Building (nicknamed &#x27;The Beehive&#x27;) in Wellington, New Zealand

