==Personal life==
While studying at University of Cincinnati, Meyer met Shelley Mather, a freshman nursing student, at Sigma Chi&#x27;s Derby Days philanthropy event. They married in 1986. The Meyers have three children: Nicole (&quot;Nicki&quot;), Gisela (&quot;Gigi&quot;) and Nathan (&quot;Nate&quot;). His daughters played Division I volleyball: Nicki played for Georgia Tech, and Gigi played for Florida Gulf Coast. He is a practicing Roman Catholic.

