<doc id="1229123" wikidata="Q5601271" url="?curid=1229123" title="Greatest Hits (Sublime album)">
<text>Greatest Hits is the first of Sublime&#x27;s compilation albums released after frontman Bradley Nowell&#x27;s death. It was released in 1999.

The enhanced CD contained two music videos: &quot;What I Got&quot; and &quot;Wrong Way&quot;.

